pageContext.description: No. 200: length 86; weight 2; Plain head, irregularly faceted. smooth even, dark brown patina, No. 201: length 82.5; weight 3; 3 incisions on head, 3 vertical lines of 5 dots on neck. corroded & uneven. patches of dark brown patina on bright metal., No. 202: length 90; weight 3; 3 incisions on head, 3 vertical lines of 5 dots on neck. smooth, very slightly corroded. dark tarnished metal., No. 203: length 87; weight 3; 3 incisions on head. no neck. slightly corroded. dark brown patina., No. 204: length 91; weight 3; corroded head. 3 vertical lines of 5 dots on neck. corroded & uneven. patches of black on bright metal., No. 205: length 77; weight 3; corroded all over & any ornamentation obliterated. Dark brown patina & metal showing through., No. 206: length 101; weight 5; 3 incisions on head, 3 vertical lines of 6 dots on neck. smooth & even. Black patina with some metal showing through., No. 207: length 87; weight 4; 3 incisions on head, 3 vertical lines of 6 dots on neck. corroded. Black patina & bright metal., No. 208: length 86; weight 4; 3 incisions on head, 3 vertical lines of 6 dots on neck. smooth. dark tarnished metal., No. 209: length 96; weight 4; 3 incisions on head, 3 vertical lines of 4 dots divised by 3 grooves. each groove terminates in a dot. smooth & even. Bright metal all over.
